Package fun.connor.fantasy.Database

Class Database

  • java.lang.Object
    • fun.connor.fantasy.Database.Database
  • class Database
extends java.lang.Object
    The database class is currently only being used as a stand-in for my original database model. Because of many MongoDB errors, I removed it and its connection via Morphia. The methods in this class are not significant. Actual information on the database model can be found in the documentation for the DataAccessObject.
